      "beast_baseline": "I'm not really sure why you keep bringing up goblins. I'm just trying to understand the legal implications for my company. \n\nCan we just stick to the contract? If the utility company is negligent, but the failure still impacts our ability to perform, how does a court usually weigh that \"reasonable control\" standard?",
